                        <p>
                         UCR's Chief Compliance Officer coordinates the campus's efforts under the
                         <a href="/ethics-compliance-program" target="_blank" title="Ethics &amp;amp; Compliance Program">
                          University of California's ethics and compliance program plan
                         </a>
                         .
                        </p>
